---
title: Nashville-Style Hot Chicken with Creamy Mac and Cheese
description: Get ready for the heat! Crispy chicken thighs get a fiery dredge in Nashville-inspired hot sauce. But don't worry, you can cool down your taste buds with a creamy side of one-pot mac and cheese!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nashville-style-hot-chicken-69780f76.jpg
